Jack Bailey (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Bailey_(actor) 0 John Wesley Bailey, Jr. (September 15, 1907 – February 1, 1980) was an American actor and daytime game show host. He was born in Hampton, Iowa, and died in Santa Monica, California. John_Wesley_Bailey , Jr. ( September_15_,_1907 – February_1_,_1980 ) was an_American_actor and daytime_game_show_host .
